WEBVTT

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:32.040
she published over 30 children's books.

00:01:33.080 --> 00:01:35.856
Posthumously, the book she wrote
with our daughter Paris,

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:37.496
called "Dear Girl,"

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:41.000
reached the number one position
on the "New York Times" bestseller list.

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:45.160
She was a self-described tiny filmmaker.

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:48.776
She was 5'1" and her films
were not that long.

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:49.816
(Laughter)

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:54.240
Her films exemplified her natural ability
to gather people together.

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:57.656
She was also a terrific public speaker,

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:00.816
talking with children
and adults of all ages